I"$<h1 id="문제-설명">문제 설명</h1>

<p>문자열 s의 길이가 4 혹은 6이고, 숫자로만 구성돼있는지 확인해주는 함수, solution을 완성하세요. 예를 들어 s가 “a234”이면 False를 리턴하고 “1234”라면 True를 리턴하면 됩니다.</p>

<p>제한 사항</p>

<ul>
  <li>s는 길이 1 이상, 길이 8 이하인 문자열입니다.</li>
</ul>

<p>입출력 예</p>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>s</th>
      <th>return</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>“a234”</td>
      <td>false</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>“1234”</td>
      <td>true</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">solution</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">s</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">s</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">4</span> <span class="ow">or</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">s</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">6</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">s</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">isdigit</span><span class="p">()</span>
    <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="k">return</span> <span class="bp">False</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
